football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paraguay_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 804, \"end\": 809, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diego_Columbus\", \"score\": 0.9700368471236585, \"rank\": 0.029665288172653126, \"text\": \"Diego\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diego_Columbus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diego_Columbus\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They seemed destined to secure progress to the last four until Adel popped up on 88 minutes for the Pharaohs when he emerged unmarked to head home from Zizo's pinpoint cross.\", \"from\": 857, \"to\": 1031, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1009, \"end\": 1013, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ahmed_Sayed\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.0740956754528784e-14, \"text\": \"Zizo\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ahmed_Sayed\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ahmed_Sayed\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Extra-time was a non-event amid tiring limbs and minds, but Egypt had the final say as Marcelo P\\u00e9rez - the only player who failed to convert from the spot - saw his penalty brilliantly saved by Hamza Alaa before Adel converted the winning kick to give his side a 5-4 shoot-out victory.\", \"from\": 1033, \"to\": 1318, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1093, \"end\": 1098, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Egypt_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9388368990077344e-18, \"text\": \"Egypt\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Egypt_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Egypt_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Scenes of jubilation greeted Adel from his country's fans with Egypt progressing to a last-four meeting with hosts France or Argentina in Lyon on Monday evening.\", \"from\": 1320, \"to\": 1481, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1383, \"end\": 1388, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Egypt_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9388368990077344e-18, \"text\": \"Egypt\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Egypt_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Egypt_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1435, \"end\": 1441, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 5.095460218898339e-13, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1445, \"end\": 1454, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999999517968, \"rank\": 4.609771132128448e-11, \"text\": \"Argentina\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1458, \"end\": 1462, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympique_Lyonnais\", \"score\": 0.9999999960880359, \"rank\": 3.9118985154715444e-09, \"text\": \"Lyon\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympique_Lyonnais\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympique_Lyonnais\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Morocco meet Spain in the other men's semi-final in Marseille earlier on Monday.\", \"from\": 1483, \"to\": 1563, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1483, \"end\": 1490, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999999997726, \"rank\": 2.975356175850378e-13, \"text\": \"Morocco\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moroc